~/.bashrc.d/

The files in this directory are to be sourced in alphabetical order by a bash
startup script.

Since alphabetical order is required, the following categories are suggested:

00: System default files
10: Priority system default files
20: Variable definitions for any following scripts
30: PATH and shell configuration
40:
50: Shell helper applications
60:
70:
80:
90: Global overrides
  99: tmux or screen
